desc_short	-----								Welcome to the biggest galactic reality TV show of all time, Doctor Kvorak’s Obliteration Game. A rather peculiar single player puzzle adventure for HTC Vive, Oculus Rift or PC Desktop starring three talented alien contestants, a glamorous space chicken and a dastardly deity with an ego problem.							
developer									Freekstorm								
